Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:08.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}绝对！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:11.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}只要念著遇见爱
